# --- Submission artifacts ------------------------------------------------
# Training run outputs are *not* committed by default — only the final
# README-embedded plots and the curated jsonl should be checked in. The
# `runs/*` (not `runs/`) pattern is intentional: git cannot un-ignore files
# inside an ignored directory, so listing the directory contents lets the
# `!runs/<file>` negations actually take effect.
runs/*
!runs/README.md
!runs/training_curves.png
!runs/baseline_vs_trained.png
!runs/grpo_reward.png
!runs/llm_vs_random.png
!runs/training.jsonl

# --- Model artifacts -----------------------------------------------------
*.pt
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.gguf

# --- Local config --------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
